---
import { SOCIAL_LINKS } from '../lib/data';
import { withBase } from '../lib/url';
---

<section id="about" class="about-grid">
	<div class="about-text">
		<p>
			I'm a backend software engineer based in Dhaka, building distributed systems in Go and Rust.
			I've shipped an auth service handling 1M+ users at 30ms P99, a custom fuzzy-search address
			builder, and the CI pipelines that ship it all.
		</p>
		<p>
			I'm currently a Software Engineer at Pathao. Off the clock, I write about Go, databases, and
			performance for <a href={SOCIAL_LINKS.medium}>20,000+ monthly readers</a> on Medium.
		</p>
		<div class="links">
			<a href={SOCIAL_LINKS.email}>Email</a>
			<a href={SOCIAL_LINKS.github}>GitHub</a>
			<a href={SOCIAL_LINKS.linkedin}>LinkedIn</a>
			<a href={SOCIAL_LINKS.medium}>Medium</a>
			<a href={withBase('resume.pdf')}>Resume</a>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="about-photo">
		<img src={withBase('headshot.jpg')} alt="Rahul Reza" />
	</div>
</section>
